- --- 3. SecurityReason Note ---
Officialy SREASONRES:20090625 has been detected in:
- - OpenBSD
- - NetBSD
- - FreeBSD
- - MacOSX
- - Google Chrome
- - Mozilla Firefox
- - Mozilla Seamonkey
- - Mozilla Thunderbird
- - Mozilla Sunbird
- - Mozilla Camino
- - KDE (example: konqueror)
- - Opera
- - K-Meleon
- - F-Lock

This list is not yet closed. 


- --- 4. Fix ---
